Hello,
The American Legion Tattler Post #973 are opening their doors to the public tomorrow Monday, April 25th at 6pm to midnight. 

The event is for an Industry Night to benefit Revived Soldiers Ukraine (https://www.rsukraine.org/). This not-for-profit group provides Medical & Humanitarian Aid to Ukraine, its soldiers, and their families. 

It's open to everyone. Come on by and buy some drinks for a good cause.
